examples.translation: I was born in Turkey but I live in Germany.

glosses: to rise; of a celestial body, to appear to move upwards from below the horizon of a planet as a result of the planet's rotation.

examples.translation: The Sun hadn't yet risen when I woke up.

glosses: to emerge, come about, begin, emanate, ensue
